### 1.1. POJO (Plain Old Java Object)

Mc tiu chnh ca POJO l **i din cho mt d liu** hoc **i tng**, thng dng  truyn d liu hoc nh x d liu t/to database, JSON, XML,...

- POJO l mt class m khng chu s chi phi ca bt k framework c th no.
- Mt POJO khng c quy tc t tn c th cho cc thuc tnh v phng thc ca n.
- ![](data:image/png;base64,)
- Bn trn l mt v d v POJO. UserPojo c th s dng  bt k mt chng trnh, framework no. Nhng n tht s khng c mt quy tc no  nh ngha constructor, class state, modifier (public, private, protected, default). Do vy UserPojo class c th gp mt s rc ri khi s dng trong cc framework.
- **Truyn d liu gia cc lp** (trong Java app hoc gia backend vi frontend).

Viec truyen du lieu o day lien quan den khoi tao doi tuong phu thuoc

![](data:image/png;base64,)

- **Lm Entity trong ORM** nh Hibernate/JPA (khi thm annotation nh @Entity, @Table th n thnh "JPA Entity", nhng vn da trn POJO).

- **Tr d liu t API (DTO)**.

### 1.2 Java Bean

- JavaBean l nhng lp trong java c thit k c bit nhm tng tnh s dng li, hng i tng.
- Thc t chng l nhng lp ng gi nhiu i tng vo trong 1 i tng n (gi l bean).
- Cc lp JavaBean v c bn vn l POJO nhng cn tho m cc yu cu sau:
    - **Access levels**: cc thuc tnh trong class u c t l private v chng ch c truy xut thng qua getter, setter method.
    - **Method name**: getter v setter method tun th theo quy tc getX v setX (X l tn thuc tnh). Trong trng hp thuc tnh c kiu d liu boolean th c th t l isX.
    - **Default Constructor**: Lun tn ti mt constructor mc nh khng cha tham s u vo.
    - **Serializable**: implement Serializable interface.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

- JavaBean c th hu dng khi s dng trong cc framework ngy nay, tuy nhin vic s dng n cng c mt s hn ch nht nh m chng ta s phi chp nhn:
    - **Mutability**: cc JavaBean s khng th t c tnh cht immutable v chng phi nh ngha cc setter method.
    - **Boilerplate**: Vic trin khai getter, setter method cho ton b cc thuc tnh trong class i khi khng cn thit.
    - **No-Agrs Constructor**: Chng ta thng khng cung cp no-args constructor v c mt s thuc tnh bt buc phi c gi tr sau khi khi to, chng ta s khng th t c mc ch ny khi s dng JavaBean.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

### 1.3 Spring Bean

**Bean** l mt **i tng Java c qun l bi Spring Container**. Ni cch khc, Spring s chu trch nhim **khi to**, **cu hnh**, **qun l vng i** ca cc i tng .

- Spring Beans chnh l nhng Java Object m t  to nn khung sn ca mt Spring application.
- Spring Bean khng c g c bit, bt k object no trong Spring framework m chng ta khi to thng qua Spring container c gi l Spring Bean.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

- Spring cung cp 3 cch  cu hnh Bean:
    - **Annotation Based Configuration**  Bng vic s dng @Service hoc @Component annotations. Chi tit v Scope c th c cung cp bi @Scope annotation.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

- - **XML Based Configuration**  Bng vic to file XML Spring Configuration  config beans.
    - ![](data:image/png;base64,)
    - **Java Based Configuration**  c tch hp t Spring 3.0, chng ta c th configure Spring beans s dng chng trnh java. Mt vi annotations quan trng c s dng cho config da trn java l @Configuration, @ComponentScan v @Bean.
    - ![](data:image/png;base64,)

###  1. Spring qun l i tng thay bn

Khi bn ng k mt object thnh **bean**, Spring s:

To instance.

Gn cc ph thuc (dependencies).

Theo di vng i (khi to, hy...).

Ti s dng nu cn (singleton).

 Nu bn new MyService() bng tay, bn phi t x l mi th  trn.

###  2. H tr ****Dependency Injection (DI)****

Spring h tr **tim ph thuc t ng** (gim coupling gia cc class):

java

CopyEdit

@Servicepublic class UserService {

@Autowired

private UserRepository userRepository; // Spring t inject

}

Nu UserRepository khng phi l bean, Spring **khng th inject c**.

###  3. H tr cu hnh nng cao (Scope, Proxy, Lifecycle)

Khi object l **bean**, bn c th:

i phm vi (@Scope("prototype"), session, request, v.v.).

Thm logic khi khi to (@PostConstruct) hoc hy (@PreDestroy).

To proxy  thm AOP (Aspect-Oriented Programming), logging, security

###  4. D dng test & m rng

Cc bean c th **mock** d hn trong test.

D dng **thay th bng cu hnh khc** m khng i code.

Tng thch vi Spring Boot, AOP, Security, v.v.
